headline: The AI-Fueled Cyber Threat Boom Means These Two Stocks Will Win Big
summary: Artificial intelligence (AI) promises transformative productivity gains, but it also amplifies cybersecurity risks on an unprecedented scale. As organizations deploy AI agents closer to the edge, they introduce thousands of new endpoints. headline: CrowdStrike NordVPN Alliance Extends Threat Intelligence And Investor Interest
summary: CrowdStrike Holdings (NasdaqGS:CRWD) is partnering with NordVPN to deliver enterprise-grade threat intelligence to NordVPN users worldwide. The collaboration powers NordVPN's Threat Protection Pro feature with CrowdStrike's real-time, adversary-focused data. The move brings CrowdStrike's endpoint security expertise directly into the consumer VPN market.
